high_descs: Turn to the right to face the kitchen sink.
Pick up the egg that is in the sink.
Turn right, walk a few steps, turn right, walk a few more steps, then turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge before taking it back out and closing the door.
Turn right, walk to the stove, turn right, walk to the wall, then turn left to face the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your right then face the sink
Pick up the egg in the sink
Turn to your right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge then put in the egg then take it again
Turn right then head to the microwave on your left
Open the microwave then put in the egg then close the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled egg in the microwave

high_descs: pick up brown egg from sink
turn to walk to face fridge
chill egg in fridge, remove egg from fridge
anns.task_desc: put a chilled egg inside microwave
